1 Missing values

The distribution of missing values is shown in the heatmap below.

A heatmap showing the extend of missingness in the data. A grey entry in the heatmap corresponds to a non-missing entry in the data, while a white entry in the heatmap corresponds to a missing entry in the data. The year is reported on the left of the heatmap.
